issue.title: App crashes on initialized
issue.body: As soon as you run the app from Android studio or your phone, the app crashes. I have tried it with the "Preventing Notification Spam" branch and it only crashes when i open the map, so that's definitely the problem.

issue.title: Parse Library
issue.body:
@Borophyll @lazy784 @nonlin 

Download and extract this: https://www.parse.com/downloads/android/Parse/latest

Drag the Parse-*.jar you downloaded into your existing app's "libs" folder

I have no actual idea where the "libs" folder is, so just search in the project's directory. Make sure you've built gradle at least once when you search for it.
